data.description: Come see this amazing 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom well-maintained home. This two-story home is located on a corner lot at the entrance of the Subdivision and is great for entertaining family and friends with its open floor plan. The eat in Kitchen features hard wood floors, granite counter tops and offers a breakfast bar. The kitchen is open to the family room and a living room that features ornamental molding. The bonus loft upstairs is ideal for a home office or second family room. The Owner's suite includes a trey ceiling and private bath has a separate shower, garden tub, dual vanities and a walk-in closet. The second floor also includes two additional bedrooms, one full bathroom and a laundry room. This home has a private, fenced in back yard. It is located in a great location near shopping, entertainment and GA Gwinnett College. Easy access to Hwy 316 and Sugarloaf Parkway.
